  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Also, at 10th level, you learn to make use of your signature Jutsu Necrosis beyond your base Assassination Techniques. When you would trigger your Lethal Attack class feature while casting Necrosis you can choose to activate any one of the following effects;</p><ul><li><p>The target makes any saving throw against Necrosis, at disadvantage.</p></li><li><p>The target loses concentration on one jutsu it is concentrating on at random.</p></li><li><p>The target has its movement speed reduced to 0 until the beginning of its next turn.</p></li></ul>",
